p) makes the situation even worse than it was. With this change hybrids become an even more attractive option as tanks in PoP than they already would have been. By the same logic, the warrior's value as a tank in PoP is further diminished by the new CH that will not fill a low hp warrior's hp bar.<br>
<br>
Sure, most of the time warriors won't be so low on hp that the new CH fails to fill the bar, but when it does fail to fill that bar it might as well be a hybrid tanking that mob. Factor in the current reasons hybrids are being used as tanks and the state of the warrior class suffers yet again. <p><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=241916" TARGET = "_NEW" TITLE="View My Magelo Profile"><B>Ulua O'Maui</B></A>, Woodelf Warlord <br>
